definitions.definition: A playoff in the round with only four players or teams left, the stage before the final .
A competition that narrows a field of contestants ( semifinalists ) to a set of finalists , for a subsequent final .

main_definition: ( sports ) A playoff in the round with only four players or teams left, the stage before the final .
